quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,187,"Ubibutse igihe Imana yapfundika amasezerano na bamwe bahawe igitabu c’Imana gitagatifu ibabwira iti:- ni ngombwa iki gitabu mugisigurire abantu kandi ntimukinyegeze, mugabo bagitaye inyuma y’imigongo yabo baca bitorera amatungo makeyi gusa, rero n’ububisha bumeze gute bw’uko gutora"
  3,188,"Ntiwikeke yuko bamwe banezerejwe n’ibintu bibi bagize bagakunda yuko bahayagizwa kuvyo batagize, ntiwipfuze yuko bazokizwa n’ibihano bizoba biri kuribo kandi bibabaza cane"
  3,189,"N’ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi nubw’Imana, n’Imana niyo nyene ububasha buri hejuru y’ibintu vyose"
  3,190,"Mukuremwa kw’Amajuru n’Isi, n’ikurikiranwa kw’Ijoro n’Umutaga, hariho ivyemezo ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  3,191,"Abibuka Imana yabo y’ukuri nabo bahagaze canke bicaye canke baryamye n’ukwibuka iremwa ry’Amajuru hamwe n’Isi, bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu ntiwabiremye ibi vyose ngo bibe ivy’impfagusa, ahubwo iteka nirwawe, rero n’udukingire n’ibihano vyo mu muriro udahera"
  3,192,"Muremyi wacu, bamwe uzokwinjiza mumuriro udahera ntakundi uzoba waba kengereye kandi ntihazoba abafasha kubera ubwo buhemu bw’imitima yabo"
  3,193,"Muremyi wacu, twebwe twumvise umuhamagazi ahamagara yuko twogendera ubu Isilamu n’ukwemera Umuremyi wanyu natwe turemera, Muremyi wacu n’utugirire ikigongwe kubicumuro vyacu nukuduha nagurira amakosa yacu, kandi tuze dusandabe turi kumwe n’abantu beranda"
  3,194,"Muremyi wacu, n’uduhe ivyo watwemereye bivuye kuntumwa zawe zose, kandi ntudutetereze kuri uwo musi w’imperuka, ntankeka kuri wewe ntuta indagano zawe"